# Integrations

## Export outputs (this repo)

| Platform | Output | Consumer |
|----------|--------|----------|
| windows | PNG frame sequence + instructions | RealWorld Cursor Editor → `.ani` |
| linux | Plymouth theme ZIP | `/usr/share/plymouth/themes/` |
| chrome | MV3 extension folder | `chrome://extensions` load unpacked |

PNG/GIF also via `P5CanvasRef` at 32×32 / 48×48 for Next.js `loading.tsx` or design systems.

